    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Cunctis hominibus haec praeparavit origo <lb n="2"/>reddere pignus terrae quod de&amp;lt;de&amp;gt;rat olim <lb n="3"/>emissis omnibus poenis penetrat spiritus caelo <lb n="4"/>sanctae maiestati dare <expan><abbr>ratione</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> de factis <lb n="5"/>comparavit <expan><abbr>ista</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>memoria</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> cuius capitula continent versus <lb n="6"/>et fecit venerandae memorabili virginiae suae <lb n="7"/>nudum destituit coniugis aegra latus <lb n="8"/>titulus decla&amp;lt;ra&amp;gt;t nostrum contubernium annos <lb n="9"/>infantili aetate annos complebimus <note>sic</note> istos XXXIII <expan><abbr>men</abbr><ex>ses</ex></expan> VIII <lb n="10"/>numquam l<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>esit</abbr></expan> numquam animos mariti <lb n="11"/>Victoria felix precibus tuis sedem prior possides istam <lb n="12"/>saucius his titulis singula signa dedi </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Deposita VIII Idus <expan><abbr>Ian</abbr><ex>uarias</ex></expan> post <expan><abbr>cons</abbr><ex>ulatum</ex></expan> Sergi et Nigriniani
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Sarkophagkasten. Z. 14 befindet sich auf dem Sockel. Z. 1-13: Akrostichon CRESCENTINVS. Z. 14: am Zeilenanfang ein Alpha, am Zeilenende ein Omega.</p>
            </div>
